How to download steps:
1> open the link you will go to google drive
2> After that there are two folders of covid and non covid download them.
3> After that you will get their Zip file on your download folder after that Extract them using winarr or winzip which u guys used and extract those files where you want.
4> In this way you can download a dataset for the same or another too.

